sql:
SELECT AVG(temp_avg_all4) AS average_temperature
FROM sensor_data
WHERE sensor_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- "mastermind" refers to the user who accessed the data; 
- "treasure trove of knowledge" refers to the data points with a processing status of 'completed';
- "precious gem" refers to the data point with the highest processing status (completed) and its corresponding ID;
- "prophecy the model foretold" refers to the predicted value from the model.
